# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Adjusted Position)

## Summary
The piano overlay has been lowered to simulate a better 3D perspective.

## New Features
- **3D Perspective**: The piano is now a shorter strip (100px high) at the very bottom.
- **Top-Down Interaction**: This alignment encourages you to "tap the tops" of the keys, similar to a real piano viewed from above.
- **Labels**: Keys are clearly labeled (C, D, E...).
- **History**: Recent keys are logged on screen.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
